---
title: Caribbean Bean Chilli Bowl with Toasted Coconut & Tomato Salsa
description: Serve up the flavours of Caribbean cuisine in a colourful and exciting bowl! With fluffy basmati rice and a sauce loaded with veggies and beans, all topped off with a scattering of charred corn kernels, this bowl gets better with every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-bean-bowl-b732fb3f.jpg
